Token.Abstract: The default data source for the VirtuosoSubscriptionManager.
Requests a synchronous metadata lookup for a known asset ID

Parameter.Name: assetID
Parameter.Abstract: The asset ID representing an asset to lookup

Parameter.Name: knownData
Parameter.Abstract: The known metadata received by the backplane for this asset. May be used as a reference to provide additional missing data.

ReturnValue.Abstract: A NSDictionary object containing all required keys, as defined in the data source protocol

Token.Abstract: Indicates that an asset was succesfully processed

Parameter.Name: metadata
Parameter.Abstract: A NSDictionary object containing, at a minimum, metadata values for the keys defined in the data source protocol. Any additional data provided by the Backplane or the External Catalog during a metadata lookup may also be defined, and Callers can access custom catalog data in this manner.

Token.Abstract: Indicates a new VirtuosoAsset item has been created

Parameter.Name: asset
Parameter.Abstract: A VirtuosoAsset item that has just been created by the Subscription Manager
